MojoX-Renderer-Xslate
=====================

This module provides a Text::Xslate renderer for Mojo.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Mojo
    Test::Mojo
    Test::More
    Text::Xslate

